<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row mb-5 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h1 class="fw-bold text-success display-5">Painel do Parceiro</h1>
            <p class="text-muted fs-5">Olá, <strong>{{usuario.nome}}</strong>. Confira o impacto ambiental da sua unidade.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-md-end">
            <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline-danger rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold shadow-sm">
                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right me-2"></i>Sair
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 h-100 bg-white">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-success text-white rounded-3 p-3 me-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-capsule fs-3"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Medicamentos</h6>
                </div>
                <h2 class="fw-bold">{{stats.totalRecebido}}</h2>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Total de itens recebidos</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 h-100 bg-white">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-3 p-3 me-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-water fs-3"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Preservação</h6>
                </div>
                <h2 class="fw-bold">{{stats.kgEvitados}}</h2>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">De resíduos fora do esgoto</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 h-100 bg-white border-start border-success border-5">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-warning text-dark rounded-3 p-3 me-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill fs-3"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Status</h6>
                </div>
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Ouro</h2>
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Nível de engajamento ambiental</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-5 bg-white h-100">
                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill text-success me-2"></i>Seu Ponto no Mapa</h4>
                <div class="p-4 bg-light rounded-4 mb-4">
                    <p class="mb-1"><strong>Endereço Cadastrado:</strong> {{usuario.endereco}}</p>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Sua farmácia aparece no mapa para todos os usuários de Cotia.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                    <a href="/coletas" class="btn btn-custom py-3 text-white">
                        <i class="bi bi-map me-2"></i>Ver ou Editar Localização
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 bg-dark text-white h-100">
                <h5 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-success">Guia de Procedimentos</h5>
                <ul class="list-unstyled small">
                    <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 mt-1"></i>
                        <span>Receba apenas medicamentos domiciliares.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-start">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 mt-1"></i>
                        <span>Mantenha as bombonas lacradas.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-0 d-flex align-items-start">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2 mt-1"></i>
                        <span>Sempre utilize luvas no manejo.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-top border-secondary">
                    <p class="x-small opacity-50 mb-0 text-center">FATEC Cotia & Cogitare - 2026</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>